room_title: Escape room "Locked Up" by Exithis Pensacola in Pensacola
room_description: You’ve been framed for murder and are scheduled for death row in the morning. You’ve just learned that the warden is responding to a disturbance giving you the opportunity to make your escape—but you only have one hour to shed your shackles, release the chained cell block door, and scour the wardens’s quarters for a secret escape route.
